room_title: Escape room "Top Secret" by Amazing Escape Room Cherry Hill in Collingswood
room_address: 2050 Springdale Rd Suite 200 Cherry Hill, NJ 08003
room_description: An unidentified object was discovered on base. Although they were ordered to quarantine the object, we believe at least one agent disobeyed the quarantine. After that, agents became paranoid, changing access codes and, for some reason, protecting one particular item. We need you to learn what you can about this unit, gain access to everything you can and recover the item they've been protecting. It's government property and a matter of national security!
